ntent = go_to_url_tool(url)\\\\n    print(f\"Content from {url}:\\\\\\\\n{page_content}\\\\\\\\n\")\\'}}]'}], 'tool_calls': None, 'raw': None, 'token_usage': None}, {'role': <MessageRole.TOOL_RESPONSE: 'tool-response'>, 'content': [{'type': 'text', 'text': 'Observation:\\nExecution logs:\\nContent from https://www.explorenicecotedazur.com/en/explore/activities-nice-cote-dazur/hiking/multi-day-itineraries/long-distance-hiking-routes/:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \"action\": \"go_to_url_tool(url=\\'https://www.explorenicecotedazur.com/en/explore/activities-nice-cote-dazur/hiking/multi-day-itineraries/long-distance-hiking-routes/\\')\",\\n  \"observation\": \"Error navigating to https://www.explorenicecotedazur.com/en/explore/activities-nice-cote-dazur/hiking/multi-day-itineraries/long-distance-hiking-routes/: Invalid URL\",\\n  \"reward\": 0.0\\n}\\n```\\n\\n\\nContent from https://www.gr-infos.com/en/gr52.htm:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \"action\": \"go_to_url_tool(url=\\'https://www.gr-infos.com/en/gr52.htm\\')\",\\n  \"observation\": \"Tile: GR\\\\u00ae52 From Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes)\\\\n            [Start of page]\\\\n\\\\n| GR France. Long Hiking Trails. Long Distance Footpaths | GR\\\\u00ae52From Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) | Chemins de Grandes Randonnees |\\\\n\\\\nThe GR\\\\u00ae52 is an iconic long-distance hiking trail spanning approximately 214 kilometers, offering an unforgettable journey through the breathtaking landscapes of the Alpes-Maritimes and the Mercantour National Park. This route begins in Entraunes and concludes in Menton, passing through remarkable locations such as Saint-Dalmas-le-Selvage, Isola, the Merveilles Valley and Sospel.\\\\n\\\\n[IMAGE: GR\\\\u00ae52 From Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes)]\\\\n\\\\n[IMAGE: GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 1]\\\\n\\\\n| GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 2 |\\\\n\\\\n[IMAGE: GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 3][IMAGE: GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 4][IMAGE: GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 5][IMAGE: GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 6][IMAGE: GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 7]\\\\n\\\\n| GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 9 \\\\u00a9 GPX Private use only |\\\\n\\\\nDistance: 214km, Elevation maximum: 2714m, Elevation minimum: 2m, Elevation gain uphill: 12571m\\\\n\\\\nIGN Maps: Haute Tinee 2 Isola 2000 PN du Mercantour (3640ET). Moyenne Tinee la Colmiane-Valdeblore PN du\\\\n\\\\nMercantour (3641ET). Vallees de la Bevera and des Paillons PN du Mercantour (3741ET). Vallee de la Vesubie PN du Mercantour (3741OT). Nice Menton Cote d\\'Azur (3742OT). Vallee de la Roya Vallee des\\\\n\\\\nMerveilles PN du Mercantour (3841OT). Cote d\\'Azur - Riviera dei Fiori (ASF1). Vallee des merveilles - Val Vermenagna (ASF4). Argentera - Mercantour (ASF5).\\\\n\\\\nThe journey begins in Entraunes, a small village nestled in the heart of the mountains. From the start, hikers are immersed in a preserved natural environment, with panoramic views of the surrounding peaks. The trail climbs gradually, offering varied landscapes ranging from alpine meadows to dense forests.\\\\n\\\\nContinuing towards Saint-Dalmas-le-Selvage, the GR\\\\u00ae52 crosses high mountain landscapes, with altitudes sometimes reaching more than 2,700 meters. Saint-Dalmas-le-Selvage is one of the highest villages in the Alpes-Maritimes, offering authentic charm and breathtaking views. The trail then continues to Isola, another picturesque village, known for its Isola 2000 ski resort.\\\\n\\\\nOne of the highlights of the GR\\\\u00ae52 is undoubtedly the crossing of the Vall\\\\u00e9e des Merveilles. This valley is famous for its rock carvings dating back to the Bronze Age, with around 40,000 carvings spread across 4,000 rocks. Hikers can discover depictions of human figures, animals, and mysterious symbols, offering a fascinating insight into prehistoric life.\\\\n\\\\nAfter the Vall\\\\u00e9e des Merveilles, the path descends towards Sospel, a charming medieval village located in a green valley. Sospel is known for its old bridge, a fortified medieval structure that spans the B\\\\u00e9v\\\\u00e9ra river. It\\\\u2019s an ideal place for a break, with its welcoming cafes and picturesque streets.\\\\n\\\\nThe GR\\\\u00ae52 ends in style in Menton, a coastal town renowned for its lush gardens and mild climate. Hikers are rewarded with spectacular views of the Mediterranean Sea, marking the end of an extraordinary adventure through the Alpes-Maritimes and the Mercantour National Park.\\\\n\\\\n| **Registration** Accommodation or business owner on or near a GR\\\\u00ae, you can appear on GR-INFOS For your registration, you can send me by email (papadimitriou4@gmail.com): your address and phone number, your website (Facebook page), a brief description with 5 beautiful photos of your establishment. Registration price : 50\\\\u20ac/2 years or 100\\\\u20ac/5 years per GR\\\\u00ae or GRP\\\\u00ae. Renewable. |\\\\n\\\\n| GR52 Hiking from Entraunes to Menton (Alpes-Maritimes) 10 |\\\\n\\\\nGR\\\\u00ae5 From Luxembourg to Mediterranean sea\\\\n\\\\nGR\\\\u00ae51 Balcony of Mediterranean sea\\\\n\\\\nGR\\\\u00ae56 Around Ubaye Valley (Alpes-de-Haute-Provence, Alpes-Maritimes)\\\\n\\\\nGR\\\\u00ae69 La Routo\\\\n\\\\nGR\\\\u00ae510 8 Valleys trail (Alpes-Maritimes)\\\\n\\\\nGR\\\\u00ae653A Via Aurelia\\\\n\\\\n[IMAGE: Mon GR]It is advisable to \",\\n  \"reward\": 1.0\\n}\\n```\\n\\n\\nContent from https://www.alltrails.com/france/alpes-maritimes/nice:\\n\\n```json\\n{\\n  \"action\": \"go_to_url_tool(url=\\'https://www.alltrails.com/france/alpes-maritimes/nice\\')\",\\n  \"observation\": \"Tile: alltrails.com\\\\n            [Start of page]\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n\\\\n[End of page]\\\\n        \",\\n  \"reward\": 1.0\\n}\\n```\\n\\n\\nContent from https://www.komoot.com/guide/1524427/hiking-around-nice:\\n\\